Source code for the twitter-to-pfif converter
This is a simple webservice to convert the latest data on Twitter to PFIF.

1) Searches for Haiti TtT tags via search.twitter.com (See epic colorodo for the spec:  http://epic.cs.colorado.edu/helping_haiti_tweak_the_twe.html)
2) Converts the results from twitter to PFIF
3) I have a cron job that passes the latest max_id to this webservice, and posts the results to haiticrisis.appspot.com/developers

author     Chirag Shah <chiragshah1@gmail.com>
